&lt;p&gt;Deputy Head of Clinical Technology 8A&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;University Hospitals of North Midlands NHS Trust are currently seeking to appoint an experienced and highly motivated Healthcare Scientist and Clinical Technologist as Deputy Head of Department within Clinical Technology.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reporting to the head of department this is a key leadership role and therefore applicants will need to demonstrate well developed leadership and management abilities as well as strong specialist knowledge and experience in one or more of the key areas of clinical engineering.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will lead and manage operational activities within the department and support a wide range of technical activities and projects related to the use and management of medical technologies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will also demonstrate a track record of proactive leadership and be committed to his own and others’ continuous development and improvement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameDavid ButlerJob titleHead of Clinical TechnologyEmail addressdave.butler@uhnm.nhs.ukTelephone number01782 672338Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Alternatively contact Lisa Nixon&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;lisa.nixon@uhns.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
